Aku hanya sedikit sedih.

402
00:28:31,835 --> 00:28:33,211
Semua bangkit.

403
00:28:34,087 --> 00:28:36,548
Silakan duduk.

404
00:28:53,022 --> 00:28:54,441
Biarkan persidangan dimulai.

405
00:29:04,868 --> 00:29:06,286
Kasus 2025-Noh-1361775,
Terdakwa Kim Su-jeong.

406
00:29:08,830 --> 00:29:10,415
{\an8}TABEL PERTAHANAN

407
00:29:10,498 --> 00:29:14,419
{\an8}Ya.

408
00:29:14,502 --> 00:29:16,588
Pada contoh pertama kasus ini,
Terdakwa Kim Su-jeong dibebaskan

409
00:29:16,671 --> 00:29:17,672
